{"tid":1994665,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翠華盈警去年度虧損最少1.6億元 本地客銳減 老鼠係翠華麵包不可分割嘅一部分","createTime":"2020-04-29T15:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T00:44:44.000Z","uid":125168,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fd209ed89a2d0c47560ba76296002722543d1963","tid":1994665,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"翠華盈警去年度虧損最少1.6億元<br />\n2020-04-29 HKT 23:01<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523517-20200429.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523517-20200429.htm&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw2E7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=f51ff9dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523517-20200429.htm&h=9eb83ec1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523517-20200429.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2sRUZtd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2sRUZtd.jpg&h=9649bb67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翠華集團預期，截3月底止年度將錄得虧損約1.6億至1.8億元，2019年度則錄得除稅後溢利約471萬元。<br />\n<br />\n集團解釋，虧損主要由於部分資產預計錄得一次性撇銷及減值虧損等非現金性項目合共約2千萬元至3千萬元；資產折舊及攤銷合共約1億元。<br />\n<br />\n另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">自去年6月中旬起及新型冠狀病毒大流行以來，入境旅客及出外用膳巿民銳減令集團收益下跌</span>，食材成本等經營成本亦持續上漲。"},{"pid":"75a1c55df335df9f94f44dea847f3b6d925f33c0","tid":1994665,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:38:07.000Z","msg":"[緊急] 5月2日截止！選民登記自動波填表機(懶人專用)：<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2F&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw2E7lpprR278wgWha8tNVfY%3D&h=c371810b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjgNzZN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYjgNzZN.gif&h=6369043d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N6Cw1ER.jpg\" data-t